Theresa M. Stone - Former Executive Vice President and Treasurer, Massachusetts Institute of Technology
William G. Jurgensen - Former Chief Executive Officer Nationwide Insurance

As of May 15, 2017[95]
Business[edit]




NZ All Blacks Mens XV's Shirt


In the United States, AIG is the largest underwriter of commercial and industrial insurance.[96]
AIG offers property casualty insurance, life insurance, retirement products, mortgage insurance and other financial services.[97] In the third quarter of 2012, the global property-and-casualty insurance business, Chartis, was renamed AIG Property Casualty. SunAmerica, life-insurance and retirement-services division, was renamed AIG Life and Retirement, other existing brands continue to be used in certain geographies and market segments.[97][98]
