American International Group, Inc. Key Developments

American International Group, Inc., Board Meeting, Jul 12, 2017
Jul 18 17
American International Group, Inc., Board Meeting, Jul 12, 2017. Agenda: To consider executive appointment.


AIG Announces the Appointment of Seraina Macia as Executive Vice President and Chief Executive Officer of Planned Technology-Focused Subsidiary
Jul 13 17
American International Group, Inc. announced the appointment of Seraina Macia as Executive Vice President and Chief Executive Officer (CEO) of a new planned subsidiary that aims to transform the way that AIG delivers and underwrites commercial insurance. The appointment is effective immediately. Ms. Macia will report to AIG President and CEO Brian Duperreault, and serve on the company's Executive Leadership Team (ELT). Ms. Macia joins AIG from Hamilton USA, where she was appointed CEO in 2016.


American International Group, Inc. Appoints Peter Zaffino as Executive Vice President and Global Chief Operating Officer, Effective August 1, 2017
Jul 5 17
American International Group, Inc. (AIG) announced the appointment of Peter Zaffino as Executive Vice President, Global Chief Operating Officer effective August 1, 2017. Mr. Zaffino joins AIG after serving as Chief Executive Officer of Marsh LLC and as Chairman of the Risk and Insurance Services segment of Marsh & McLennan Companies, Inc. since 2015. He was also a member of MMC Executive Committee since 2008.


